, Turkish race car driver\nBULLET::::- 1981 – Matt Kirk, Canadian football player\nBULLET::::- 1981 – Barbora Špotáková, Czech javelin thrower\nBULLET::::- 1981 – Ben Utecht, American football player\nBULLET::::- 1982 – Lizzy Caplan, American actress\nBULLET::::- 1982 – Ignacio Carrasco, Mexican footballer\nBULLET::::- 1983 – Marcus Burghardt, German cyclist\nBULLET::::- 1983 – Katherine Ryan, UK-based Canadian comedian, presenter\nBULLET::::- 1983 – Cheryl, English singer and TV personality\nBULLET::::- 1984 – Fantasia Barrino, American singer-songwriter and actress\nBULLET::::- 1984 – Tunku Ismail Idris, Crown Prince of Johor, Malaysia\nBULLET::::- 1985 – Trevor Ariza, American basketball player\nBULLET::::- 1985 – Michael Phelps, American swimmer\nBULLET::::- 1985 – Fabiana Vallejos, Argentinian footballer\nBULLET::::- 1986 – Alicia Fox, American wrestler, model, and actress\nBULLET::::- 1986 – Fredy Guarín, Colombian footballer\nBULLET::::- 1986 – Nicola Pozzi, Italian footballer\nBULLET::::- 1986 – Allegra Versace, Italian-American businesswoman\nBULLET::::- 1987 – Ryan Cook, American baseball player\nBULLET::::- 1987 – Andrew Hedgman, New Zealand runner\nBULLET::::- 1988 – Elisa Jordana, American singer-songwriter, radio and TV personality\nBULLET::::- 1989 – Asbel Kiprop, Kenyan runner\nBULLET::::- 1989 – Steffen Liebig, German rugby player\nBULLET::::- 1989 – David Myers, Australian footballer\nBULLET::::- 1990 – N, South Korean singer\nBULLET::::- 1998 – Tom Davies, English footballer\nBULLET::::- 350 – Nepotianus, Roman ruler\nBULLET::::- 710 – Erentrude, Frankish abbess\nBULLET::::- 888 – Æthelred, archbishop of Canterbury\nBULLET::::- 945 – Ki no Tsurayuki, Japanese writer and poet (b. 872)\nBULLET::::- 1181 – Hugh de Kevelioc, 5th Earl of Chester, Welsh politician (b. 1147)\nBULLET::::- 1224 – Adolf of Osnabrück, German monk and bishop (b. 1185)\nBULLET::::- 1278 – Pierre de la Broce, French courtier\nBULLET::::- 1337 – Eleanor de Clare, English noblewo